INTERNAL: Fit a table properly

Source: R/utils.R
fit_tbl.Rd

INTERNAL: Fit a table properly

Usage

fit_tbl(table)

Arguments

table

A flextable object to fit.

Value

A object of class flextable, autofit if interactive or HTML output, 6.5 inches otherwise.

Examples

flextable::flextable(mtcars) |>
  fit_tbl()
